“Register of LLPs” means a register of LLPs established and maintained by the 
Authority in accordance with section 126 of the Act of 2015; 

“Regulation” means a regulation in these Regulations; 

“relevant business” means (a) a partnership of solicitors, or (b) a legal 
partnership in accordance with section 99 of the Act of 2015; 

“relevant date” means the date specified in an authorisation given by the 
Authority from which the authorisation shall have effect; 

